<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c1">" حافظ"</span>. <span class="c1">"المهرة"</span> <span class="c2">(١٠/ ٣٥)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
